schemas.name: type.gql
schemas.content:
type Posyandu {
  _key: String
  name: String
  rw: String
}

type Balita {
  _key: String
  name: String
  gakin: String
  rw: String
  jk: String
  tl: String
  ortu: String
  rt: String
  posy: String
  penimbangan: [BalitaBB]
  inactive: Boolean
}

type BalitaBB {
  _key: String
  balita: String
  tgl: String
  bb: Float
  tb: Float
}

type Query {
  getPosyanduList: [Posyandu],
  posyandu(_key: String): Posyandu,
  balita(posy: String): [Balita],
  balitaBB(_key: String, tgl:String): BalitaBB
}

type Mutation {
  mutateBalitaBB(balita: String!, bb: Float!, tb: Float!, tgl: String!): BalitaBB
  mutatePosy(_key: String!, name: String!, rw: String!): Posyandu
  mutateBalita(_key: String!, name: String!, gakin: String, jk: String!, tl: String!, ortu: String, rt: String, posy: String!, rw: String, inactive: Boolean): Balita
}
